#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.fillna.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.groupby.DataFrameGroupBy.fillna"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:1 of
msgid "Fill NA/NaN values using the specified method"
msgstr "使用指定方法填充 NA/NaN 值"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:3 of
msgid "value:  scalar, dict, Series, or DataFrame"
msgstr "value: 标量、字典、Series 或 DataFrame"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:4 of
msgid ""
"Value to use to fill holes (e.g. 0), alternately a dict/Series/DataFrame "
"of values specifying which value to use for each index (for a Series) or "
"column (for a DataFrame). Values not in the dict/Series/DataFrame will "
"not be filled. This value cannot be a list."
msgstr ""
"用于填充缺失值的值（例如 0），或者是一个字典/Series/DataFrame，指定每个"
"索引（对于 Series）或列（对于 DataFrame）使用哪个值。不在字典/Series/"
"DataFrame 中的值将不会被填充。该值不能是列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:8 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"method: {'backfill','bfill','ffill',None}, default None axis:   {0 or "
"'index', 1 or 'column'} limit:  int, default None"
msgstr ""
"method: {'backfill','bfill','ffill',None}，默认为 None axis:   {0 或 '"
"index', 1 或 'column'} limit: 整数，默认为 None"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:11 of
msgid ""
"If method is specified, this is the maximum number of consecutive NaN "
"values to forward/backward fill"
msgstr "如果指定了 method，则这是向前/向后填充连续 NaN 值的最大数量"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:13 of
msgid "downcast:   dict, default None"
msgstr "downcast: 字典，默认为 None"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:14 of
msgid ""
"A dict of item->dtype of what to downcast if possible, or the string ‘"
"infer’ which will try to downcast to an appropriate equal type"
msgstr ""
"一个 item->dtype 的字典，表示在可能的情况下要降级的数据类型，或者是字符串"
" 'infer'，它会尝试降级为合适的相等类型"

#: maxframe.dataframe.groupby.fill.fillna:17 of
msgid "return: DataFrame or None"
msgstr "返回：DataFrame 或 None"

